content: I'm actually a huge fan of Billie Eilish, and I was lucky enough to score floor seats at her concert, which made the whole experience even more electrifying! I went with my best friend, Rachel, and we had a blast singing along to every song. We even got a chance to meet Billie at the meet-and-greet session before the concert, and she was so down-to-earth and sweet. Anyway, back to food - I'm in the mood for some good seafood, do you have any recommendations near FedExField that serve fresh seafood?
